各位大佬求助一下，Mod的item怎么加载语言文件啊。MC版本1.12.2-14.23.5.2847
MCP版本Stable_39
这个是主文件Main.java
package test;

import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.Mod;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.event.*;

@Mod(modid = Main.MOD_ID, name = Main.MOD_NAME, version = Main.MOD_VERSION, useMetadata = true)
public enum Main{
    INSTANCE;
    public static final String MOD_ID = "test";
    public static final String MOD_NAME = "Test";
    public static final String MOD_VERSION = "1.0.0";
    public static final String MOD_LABEL = "Test_Mod";

    @Mod.InstanceFactory
    public static Main getInstance() {
        return INSTANCE;
    }

    @Mod.EventHandler
    public void preLoad(FMLPreInitializationEvent event) {
        System.out.println("Test正在预加载。");
    }

    @Mod.EventHandler
    public void init(FMLInitializationEvent event) {
        System.out.println("Test正在初始化。");
    }

    @Mod.EventHandler
    public void postInit(FMLPostInitializationEvent event) {
        System.out.println("Test加载完毕。");
    }
}复制代码
这个是物品注册文件ItemInitializer.java
package test;

import net.minecraft.creativetab.CreativeTabs;
import net.minecraft.init.Items;
import net.minecraft.item.Item;
import net.minecraft.item.ItemStack;
import net.minecraftforge.event.RegistryEvent;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.Mod;
import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.eventhandler.SubscribeEvent;

@Mod.EventBusSubscriber(modid = Main.MOD_ID)
public final class ItemInitializer {
    public static final String NAME = "example";

    public static final CreativeTabs TAB = new CreativeTabs(Main.MOD_LABEL) {
        @Override
        public ItemStack createIcon() {
            return new ItemStack(Items.DIAMOND);
        }
    };

    public static Item item = new Item()
            .setCreativeTab(TAB)
            .setTranslationKey(NAME)
            .setRegistryName(Main.MOD_ID, NAME);

    @SubscribeEvent
    public static void registerItem(RegistryEvent.Register<Item> event) {
        event.getRegistry().register(item);
    }

}复制代码src的结构是这样的。
.
└── main
    ├── java
    │   └── test
    │       ├── ItemInitializer.java
    │       └── Main.java
    └── resources
        ├── assets
        │   └── test
        │       └── lang
        │           └── en_us.lang
        ├── mcmod.info
        └── pack.mcmeta

我进入游戏它告诉我物品名是test.example.name但是一直加载不上。
求助各位大佬怎么办啊。





